      <header class="article-header">
        
        <h1 class="article-title">cost of roof coating in Sarasota 2026</h1>
        <div class="article-meta">
          <span>📍 Sarasota, Florida</span><span class="divider"></span>
          <span>Updated January 15, 2026</span>
